title: He Doesn't Like Different Types Of Cookie

description:
Dear Steve and Shirley, I am 35 year old married woman and I have been married for three years, but, I've been with my husband for over 8 years. He was supposed to be a one night stand but he ended up rocking my world and I kept going back for more. He grew on me and I ended up falling in love with him. It's no secret that he fell in love with me first and he loves to tell people how he pursed me until I gave into him..................
